title: For Sale:  Browning Citori 12ga 725 Sporting 32
postcontent: Manufacturer: Browning  Model: Citori C725 Sporting Action: Over and Under Caliber: 12ga Bore: Perfect Barrel Length: 32 inches Finish: Blue Grips/Stock: Factory Checkered Wood with 14" lopThe Citori 725 Sporting Over/Under Shotgun specifically for winning sporting clays competition as well as trap and skeet. Browning focused much of the 725's innovative design on a low profile receiver. Positioning the barrels lower in the receiver changes the relationship of your cheek and eye to the rib, putting face, eyes, and hands closer to the center line of the gun. This "in-in" feeling results in a better fit and natural point ability. The 725's low profile receiver also improves recoil control by pushing the gun straight back into the shoulder instead of the muzzle jumping up, which makes getting an aimed, second shot off quicker. The strength of the Citori 725's receiver is not sacrificed by using undersized trunnions and narrow, tapered pins to lock up the receiver as some low profile designs do. The 725 still uses a rugged full-width hinge pin, and the transverse mounted locking bolt design of the original Citori. The Citori 725 features the Fire Lite mechanical trigger design that delivers a light, smooth pull. By not relying on inertia to reset the second hammer, a mechanical trigger ensures you get an immediate second shot, without worrying about your gun unexpectedly doubling. To prevent sporting clay shooters from getting worn down from recoil so they can still be on top of their game at the end of the day, the Citori 725 Sporting uses ported barrels and Browning's Inflex Technology recoil pad.Will ship!

There are a few light scuffs and small dings in the stock but overall it is in excellent condition. The blue is perfect from end to end and the bore is bright and shiny. The rifle was built with claw mounts and a factory fitted high quality Swarovski 6X scope with 42MM objective. This is an unbelievably beautiful and functional rifle. if you are a lefty and want the very best this is for you
